# CODEOWNERS — `llm-lab`
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Owners are pinged on PRs touching these paths.

# Default: the maintainer reviews everything.
*                    @llm-lab/maintainers

# Security-sensitive modules — same maintainer, but a second-pass review is
# required (see CONTRIBUTING.md "Security-sensitive changes").
/llm_lab/main.py     @llm-lab/maintainers
/llm_lab/db.py       @llm-lab/maintainers
/llm_lab/planner/    @llm-lab/maintainers
/llm_lab/export.py   @llm-lab/maintainers
/SECURITY.md         @llm-lab/maintainers
/THREAT_MODEL.md     @llm-lab/maintainers

# ADRs — any new ADR or amendment is reviewed by the maintainer.
/docs/adr/           @llm-lab/maintainers

# When we have a second maintainer, the @llm-lab/maintainers team will expand.
